01:13.080 --> 01:17.930
In fact I think I'm going to bring mine down to kind of a middle gray as well.

01:18.330 --> 01:26.400
And then down here in the volume section you need to click on this and select volume scatter and that

01:26.400 --> 01:30.790
will give us our volumetric lighting and you may be asking.

