It doesn't look very good.

01:32.100 --> 01:33.550
Well no it doesn't.

01:33.550 --> 01:37.560
We need to take the density down quite a bit.

01:37.650 --> 01:46.680
So instead of 1.0 Let's take it down to point 0 1 and let's see how that looks a little bit better.

01:47.010 --> 01:51.570
Let's also take the ambient occlusion factor to point 0 2.

01:51.570 --> 01:55.710
Let's try that and you may be able to hear the fan in my computer.

01:55.710 --> 01:59.370
Click on now that it's trying to render out the scene.

01:59.430 --> 02:08.070
